{"tid":1642660,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[國際] Epic CEO: Epic尊重Fortnite玩家同creator對政治/人權既言論自由","createTime":"2019-10-09T21:28:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-11T09:31:48.000Z","uid":46323,"like":124,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":51,"replies":[{"pid":"1c5b9144f0db16d261fe2713c02fa9d76f7b590a","tid":1642660,"uid":46323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T21:28:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QQsjOsQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQQsjOsQ.png&h=9887b504&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/TimSweeneyEpic/status/1181933071760789504\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FTimSweeneyEpic%2Fstatus%2F1181933071760789504&d=FZDcFY5BXo0CBgddFpFX58g7Fotki3H%2BSmgHlFrgEoM%3D&h=6257f205\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FTimSweeneyEpic%2Fstatus%2F1181933071760789504&h=882daa93\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/TimSweeneyEpic/status/1181933071760789504</a><br />\n<br />\n問: 如果有人係賽後訪問講「Free Hong Kong」, 你係咪唔會做任何野<br />\nTim Sweeney: 無錯<br />\n<br />\n問: 乜Epic唔係40%股權係騰訊咩?<br />\nTim: Epic係一間美國公司而且我先係話事人, 騰訊雖然係40%股東, 但係仲有好多其他shareholder例如員工同投資者<br />\n<br />\n問: 你可唔可以老老實實咁講, 即使將來有類似NBA既中國資金流失發生都好, 你唔會對例如個NBA既教練/爐石玩家, 做任何野<br />\n<br />\nTim: 絕對唔會。類似既野絕對唔會係我仲係 Epic CEO/話事人既時候發生。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我都唔知Tim Sweeney係想順水PR, 定係知道暴雪行咗條錯路, 拿拿臨割<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n提下大家, Epic係封咗大陸地區, 姐係話佢係咪都冇預自己賺大陸市場錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9ab4d44e5b85b9a631e34e08ba707446eb90612","tid":1642660,"uid":46323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T21:33:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc752cbc2967b8e20ba95b6f5fa66ee7a7fc593f","tid":1642660,"uid":97240,"like":36,"dislike":